        "description": "<p><em>Pillage Cosmique</em> is a variant of the arcade game <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/63912/cosmic-guerilla/\">Cosmic Guerilla</a>. It is a fixed screen shoot 'em up where the player has to stop the alien invaders that attempt to steal the fuel canisters and space ships located in the centre of the screen. The aliens start from the sides of the screen and move towards the centre where they pick up the objects and return back to where they came from. The player's task is to shoot them down before they are able to escape. If an alien is shot while carrying an object it will return to its original position. If one of the space ships are stolen, the player will lose a life. A life is also lost when hit by the projectiles dropped by the aliens. In addition to the regular aliens, there are also saucers and space monsters to watch out for.</p>",
